title: Pinstripe v2.0.1
description: Pinstripe is an emotionally charged adventure through Hell created entirely by a one-man team over the course of five years. Play as Teddy, an estranged ex-minister forced to venture through the frozen afterlife in search of his three-year-old daughter Bo, and her perverse kidnapper. Discover the dark secrets of Teddy's past, and confront his sleazy, demonic nemesis, Mr. Pinstripe.Thomas Brush, creator of award winning indie games Coma and Skinny, reveals a gorgeous art style, breathtaking
